"title": "5945: self-pity",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5945",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sorrow or despondency aroused by one's own suffering or misfortune. It can result from personal loss or suffering, hardship in God's service or the judgment of God. Its cure is to remember the goodness of God.</p>\n<h2>Examples of self-pity as a result of personal loss or suffering</h2>\n<h3>The Israelites in the wilderness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:3\">EXO 16:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:10-Exod14:12\">EXO 14:10–14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:3\">EXO 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:4-Num11:6\">NUM 11:4–11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1-Num14:4\">NUM 14:1–14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:26-Deut1:28\">DEU 1:26–1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:10-1Cor10:11\">1CO 10:10–10:11</a></p>\n<h3>Job</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:1-Job6:13\">JOB 6:1–6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:1\">JOB 10:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:1-Job3:26\">JOB 3:1–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:1-Job12:6\">JOB 12:1–12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:6-Job17:2\">JOB 16:6–17:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:9-Job30:31\">JOB 30:9–30:31</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:34\">GEN 27:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:38\">GEN 27:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:30\">2SA 15:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:2-2Kgs20:3\">2KI 20:2–20:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:2-Isa38:3\">ISA 38:2–38:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:1\">PSA 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:2-Ps73:3\">PSA 73:2–73:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13-Ps73:14\">PSA 73:13–73:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:1\">PSA 74:1</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of self-pity as a result of hardship in the service of God</h2>\n<h3>Moses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:11-Num11:15\">NUM 11:11–11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:22-Exod5:23\">EXO 5:22–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:4\">EXO 17:4</a></p>\n<h3>Elijah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jeremiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:10\">JER 15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:18\">JER 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:7-Jer20:10\">JER 20:7–20:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:14-Jer20:18\">JER 20:14–20:18</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer45:3\">JER 45:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:1-Jonah4:5\">JON 4:1–4:5</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of self-pity as a result of God's judgment</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1-Ps137:9\">PSA 137:1–137:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:1-Lam3:18\">LAM 3:1–3:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:9-Rev18:19\">REV 18:9–18:19</a> <em>The kings, merchants and sailors will be full of self-pity when they see the destruction of Babylon, because their opportunities for making wealth will be gone.</em></p>\n<h2>People calling upon others to pity them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:21\">JOB 19:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:22\">MRK 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:13\">LUK 17:13</a></p>\n<h2>Turning to God puts self-pity in its true perspective</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:5\">PSA 43:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:16-Ps73:17\">PSA 73:16–73:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:1-Ps3:4\">PSA 3:1–3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:1-Ps13:6\">PSA 13:1–13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:1-Ps37:7\">PSA 37:1–37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:23-Ps73:28\">PSA 73:23–73:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:7\">PSA 106:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:19-Lam3:26\">LAM 3:19–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:31-Lam3:33\">LAM 3:31–3:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:5\">2CO 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:3-2Cor6:10\">2CO 6:3–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:3\">JAS 1:2–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a></p>",
